# CLOSER — environment variables
# Copy to .env.local and fill in your key.

# Anthropic API key (required). Get one at https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Optional — defaults to claude-sonnet-4-6 (fast, demo-friendly).
# CLOSER_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6

# Optional but RECOMMENDED for production (Railway): Reddit app-only OAuth.
# Reddit blocks datacenter IPs on the anonymous endpoint, so without these the
# live Reddit source returns nothing in prod and the pipeline leans on samples.
# Create a "script" app at https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps (2 min) and paste:
# REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id
# REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret
